WEBVTT

00:01.971 --> 00:06.045
On a hill to the north is the largest and most splendid mosque in Turkey:...

00:06.697 --> 00:08.131
...the Kocatepe Camii.

00:11.859 --> 00:14.462
Between 1967 and 1988,...

00:14.988 --> 00:17.241
...this imposing tower was constructed...

00:17.539 --> 00:19.420
...with the help of private donations.

00:20.447 --> 00:23.219
A replica of the Blue Mosque in Istanbul,...

00:23.512 --> 00:28.160
...it has four minarets and accommodates around 20,000 worshippers.

00:30.018 --> 00:33.935
The Kocatepe mosque is both a symbol of the devoutness of the people...

00:34.520 --> 00:38.497
...as well as being an important center of communication for the entire city.

